snippet.title: Professor Layton vs. Ace Attorney - 100% Walkthrough - Part 1: Layton's Office
snippet.description: This will be a 100% walkthrough (solving all of the puzzles and collecting all of the hint coins) for Professor Layton vs. Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney. This part shows how to get Hint Coins #001, #002 and #003 and how to solve puzzle #01 Paths of Light in Layton's Office.
